quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  35,41,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ikingiye Amajuru n’Isi kugira ngo ntaveho, kuko avuyeho ntanumwe yoya kingira atariyo yonyene gusa, ntankeka rero Imana niyo ntungane n’ikigongwe cinshi gihagije"
  35,42,"Bararahiye ku Mana indahiro yabo niniya bavuga bati:- niba shikirwa n’uwubatuza ntankeka bazoba mubazo rongoka gusumba abandi bantu, mugabo mugihe bazoshikirwa n’uwuba tuza ntaco yobongereje atari uguhakana uko kuri gusa"
  35,43,"Kubera amanyama yabo kuri iy’Isi nukugira akajagari kabi kabi, nako kajagari kabi kabi ntikamanuka atari kuri beneko bakagize, none hari ikindi barorereye atari urutonde rwamyeho no ku bantu baho hambere, kandi ntuzoronka ihindagurika ry’urwo rutonde rusanzwe rw’Imana yagenye, canke ntuzosanga ihindagurika riri mubintu bisanzwe vy’Imana"
  35,44,"Mbega ntibagize urugendo kuri iy’Isi bakibonera impera n’imperuka yaba bayeho imbere yabo, kandi bakaba bari abantu bafise ubushobozi kubasumba, kandi ntakindi kintu gishobora kunanira Imana haba mw’Ijuru canke ng’aha kw’Isi, ntankeka rero Imana niyo ifise uburemyi n’ubushobozi bukwiye"
  35,45,"Iyo Imana ihana abantu kubera ivyo bakoze ntiyari gusiga n’umuntu numwe ngaha kuri iy’Isi canke n’igikoko na kimwe, mugabo Imana niyo iba rorereza kugeza k’umusi wagenywe, rero igihe c’umusi wabo kizoshika mu vy’ukuri Imana ku bantu bayo niyo ibabona"
  36,1,"Ya, Siiyn, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  36,2,Ndarahiye kuri aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’aani yateguwe neza cane
  36,3,Yuko mu vy’ukuri wewe uri muntumwa z’Imana
  36,4,Uri hejuru y’inzira igororotse
  36,5,Nimanurwa ryanyene ubushobozi n’impuhwe zihagije
  36,6,"Kugira ngo ubatuze abantu batatujijwe n’abavyeyi babo, rero nibo babaye abasamajwe"
  36,7,"Ntankeka n’ijambo ryemejwe kuri benshi muribo, kuri ivyo rero ntibavyemera"
  36,8,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twashize iminyororo kumazosi yabo kugeza kubusakanwa bwabo, rero imitwe yabo iraramye iri hejuru"
  36,9,"Twashize imbere yabo uruzitiro ruri imbere yabo n’urundi ruzitiro ruri inyuma yabo duca tubafuka mumaso yabo kuribo, kuri ivyo rero ntibabona na gatoyi"
  36,10,Nivyiza kuribo ubakebuye canke utabakebuye ntibazokwemera
  36,11,Woshobora kumutuza urya akurikira ubutumwa bw’Imana yamara kunyurwa nayo majambo y’Imana agaca atinya nyene imigisha naho atayibona rero numubwire uyo yuko ikigongwe hamwe n’impuhwe z’iteka ziri kuriwe
  36,12,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzozura abapfuye kandi twandike ibikorwa vyabo bagira ntibize bisigare inyuma, n’ibintu vyose biri mububiko bw’igitabu cerekana ibintu vyose"
  36,13,Nubagirire akarorero k’abantu bo mugisagara kanaka mugihe bashikirwa naba shikiriza butumwa
  36,14,"Mugihe twabarungikira intumwa z’Imana zibiri barazi hakana natwe duca tubongereza inguvu tuba rungikira uwugira gatatu, bababwira bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe turungitswe kuri mwebwe"
  36,15,"Nabo babishura bati:- mwebwe ntaco murimwo, atari uko muri mu bantu nkatwe, nayo nyene imigisha ntanakimwe yamanuye, mwebwe muri ababeshi gusa"
  36,16,"Bavuze bati:- Umuremyi wacu niwe afise ubumenyi atamakenga arimwo yuko twebwe twarungitswe kuri mwebwe"
  36,17,Kandi ntakiri hejuru yacu atari ugushikana ubutumwa bw’Imana buri k’umugaragaro
  36,18,"Baca bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe ntitwumvikana kubera mwebwe nimutareka twebwe tuzoba tera iminana kandi izobashikira ivuye iwacu n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  36,19,"Bavuze bati:- ukutumvikana kwanyu mwebwe nyene, yo! kuko mwibutswa mugabo mwebwe muri mu bantu mwarenze akarimbi"
  36,20,"Haciye haza umuntu ningoga na ningoga avuye kuruhande rwakure rw’ico gisagara avuga ati:- bantu banje nimukurikire izi ntumwa"
  36,21,"Nimu bakurikire babigishe batarinze kubasaba impembo iyariyo yose, mugihe abo bantu bari mubarongotse"
  36,22,"Nikuki ntosenga uwandemye, niwe ariho muzo subizwayo"
  36,23,"Mbega jewe nkurikire izindi Mana atari Imana yonyene rudende, niyaba Imana ishaka kungirira inabi, ibisabisho vyabo ntaco bizomarira n’ikintu na kimwe kandi ntibazondokora"
  36,24,Ninagira gutyo nzoba ndimu bantu bazimiye mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro
  36,25,Ntankeka jewe ndemeye Umuremyi wanyu mugabo ndabasavye mu nyumvirize
  36,26,"Ababwira ati:- niwinjire mw’Ijuru, nawe yishura ati:- iyo abantu banje babimenya"
  36,27,"Ingene Umuremyi wanje yangiriye ikigongwe nuku mpezagira, nkaba ndimu bahawe iteka ntangere"